Download TIGER shapes for New England City and Town Area

Source: R/new_england_city.R
tt_new_england_cities.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for New England City and Town Area

Usage

tt_new_england_cities(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_new_england_cities()
